text:
A small stall manned by uncle and auntie duo; and uncle is especially passionate about his food. Super confident that his chicken chop is unlike anywhere else and that really does reflect in the food that he cooks :)

Fried Rice was the old school, lightly seasoned and comes with strong wok hey and vegetables and small meat chunks type. If you love the traditional type of old-school fried rice, this is the place to go.

Support local, support their effort and skillz
